{"tid":657902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"14歲仔跳樓亡　母哭崩","createTime":"2018-05-08T13:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T03:17:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5fdf805c74d91006462f1f5d4c099f2d7b97528","tid":657902,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180508/20384464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180508%2F20384464&d=GtAXJ63CH5ngc%2FoJJJ3mSkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b3d88106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180508%2F20384464&h=be08a01c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180508/20384464</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月08日 <br />\n<br />\n14歲仔跳樓亡　母哭崩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180508/large/0507cf_tseimg_0085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180508%2Flarge%2F0507cf_tseimg_0085.jpg&h=0781430f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■14歲中二男生從高處墮下，當場證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】14歲中二姓麥男生，前晚9時許被街坊發現倒卧在大埔富善街7至13號富盛大廈地舖對上的帆布簷篷，大量流血，消防員接報到場將他抬到地下，經救護員檢驗證實不治。警員初步調查相信他從大廈高處一個單位墮下，稍後其母親驚聞噩耗，趕至現場認屍，崩潰痛哭。警方在現場未有撿獲遺書，正調查男童墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，男童在內地出生，祖籍廣東中山，在太和一間中學就讀中二。其家人疑為免睹物思人，昨日將死者的書簿等物品丟棄。校方表示，全校師生昨日獲知噩耗後極為難過及悲痛，由於事件交由警方調查，校方現階段不宜發表意見。學校已啟動「危機處理小組」為學生提供輔導，協助他們疏導情緒。校方亦已發出家長信，着家長留意情緒受困擾的學生，以便及早提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n■記者溫文學、黃麗英  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n科大實驗室洩強毒化學液　10學生疏散<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n劫鳳姐賊過關落網"},{"pid":"2d9fcdb19b859ca0a037b132b66808ab4d7482fd","tid":657902,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4de06b2ee2653f58ece6f4674960c9660bc4611","tid":657902,"uid":117225,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"睇到第二段<br />\n果段上一頁<br />\n邊個叫你落嚟香港依啲山卡啦讀咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf68c7cf0cc27a1c87bec205e2082ad28def42f4","tid":657902,"uid":144784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4de06b2ee2653f58ece6f4674960c9660bc4611","tid":657902,"uid":117225,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"睇到第二段<br />\n果段上一頁<br />\n邊個叫你落嚟香港依啲山卡啦讀咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:47:57.000Z","msg":"上一頁完又返嚟留言欣賞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6790fd6519c19b49afe779d67af0a1db5fd1e7","tid":657902,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T00:20:54.000Z","msg":"返中国啦"},{"pid":"029d3c46ef57615a713c8990722b5f5e5274e524","tid":657902,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T00:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇到第二段<br />\n果段上一頁<br />\n邊個叫你落嚟香港依啲山卡啦讀咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>上一頁完又返嚟留言欣賞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d傻仔講野都95搭8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f685fccd06aceb713c9471694b20acdf7d5dfd19","tid":657902,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T00:29:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d3e2554de30f57579ec0225db1e286686c0447f","tid":657902,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T00:30:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dee443324569a26881e6f1cc98cf142646a5b38a","tid":657902,"uid":28624,"like"